            </span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
        <div class="feature-card" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ddd6fe 0%, #c4b5fd 100%);">
            <div class="feature-icon" style="background: white;">
                <i class="fas fa-cog" style="color: #e11d48;"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="feature-title">System Settings</h3>
            <p class="feature-description">Configure system preferences, manage user permissions, and customize your hotel operations.</p>
            <span class="feature-link">
